  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/eef576c552792ca0a5003dd2db08c7ed.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/1eb7487bd16081fbc1218e24f7911810.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/1eb7487bd16081fbc1218e24f7911810.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the year 2398, a network of intelligent computers known as <strong>Nightgate</strong>, is the last remaining life form on Earth. Step into the computer and uncover what lies beyond the futuristic landscapes of Nightgate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/0b38eddd878ed177f4ef98a4acbe244e.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ceaf178a596ccef9c3b658048813320.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ceaf178a596ccef9c3b658048813320.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate hostile enemy systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge bullets and evade threats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/abdb51267ebf893cd5253686f372d3c2.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/db04552e04f9912a17fd023ee5fea331.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/db04552e04f9912a17fd023ee5fea331.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Born from an obsession with sci-fi interfaces and HUDs, Nightgate offers:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Living digital architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic structures that build as you move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique environments where no two levels are alike</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/d1f236e85614fb5bf448c0584fac7e3e.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ea5d46da687a40f7bcf53663e428031.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ea5d46da687a40f7bcf53663e428031.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game camera to capture the beauty of the digital realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pause. Snap. Save. Share.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/6769ba1f4b494731bdf1f40e1d79d435.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/7307fcc8201d0d3bb3b505b7ff8674af.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1200 height=580 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a rich soundscape of deep synths, dark pads, and minimal piano, crafted to sync perfectly with the game for a cinematic experience.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/eef576c552792ca0a5003dd2db08c7ed.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/1eb7487bd16081fbc1218e24f7911810.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/1eb7487bd16081fbc1218e24f7911810.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the year 2398, a network of intelligent computers known as <strong>Nightgate</strong>, is the last remaining life form on Earth. Step into the computer and uncover what lies beyond the futuristic landscapes of Nightgate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/0b38eddd878ed177f4ef98a4acbe244e.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ceaf178a596ccef9c3b658048813320.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ceaf178a596ccef9c3b658048813320.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate hostile enemy systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge bullets and evade threats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/abdb51267ebf893cd5253686f372d3c2.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/db04552e04f9912a17fd023ee5fea331.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/db04552e04f9912a17fd023ee5fea331.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Born from an obsession with sci-fi interfaces and HUDs, Nightgate offers:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Living digital architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic structures that build as you move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique environments where no two levels are alike</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/d1f236e85614fb5bf448c0584fac7e3e.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ea5d46da687a40f7bcf53663e428031.poster.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/5ea5d46da687a40f7bcf53663e428031.webm?t=1757782039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game camera to capture the beauty of the digital realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pause. Snap. Save. Share.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/6769ba1f4b494731bdf1f40e1d79d435.avif?t=1757782039\" width=800 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2836180/extras/7307fcc8201d0d3bb3b505b7ff8674af.avif?t=1757782039\" width=1200 height=580 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a rich soundscape of deep synths, dark pads, and minimal piano, crafted to sync perfectly with the game for a cinematic experience.</p>",
